NON SANCTIONED EXHIBITION MATCH
VENDETTA
HT: 5'6

Lifetime record (14-3)

HT: 5'4

Lifetime record (0-0)
Due to Isis love's devastating injury last week in Tag Team action, Ultimate Surrender is presenting an exhibition match up for your viewing pleasure. Next week the Tournament will continue.
Vendetta is back! Not just for this exhibition match up, but back out of retirement. She will joins the ranks of wrestlers next season.
Busty Claire Dames is new to US and enjoyed her match so much she will also return as a regular wrestler next season. Season six is already shaping up to be a great year.
title: SPECIAL EXHIBITION MATCH UP
